@startuml

title E Visa Processing And Follow Up System State Transition Diagram

initial : Initial State

state "Logged Out" {
    state "Create Account" {}
}

state "Logged In" {
    state "Apply for Visa" {}
    state "View Status" {}
    state "Check Status" {}
    state "Cancel Application" {}
    state "Modify Details" {}
    state "View Details" {}
    state "View Purpose" {}
    state "Give Feedback" {}
}

state "Final State" {}

Logged Out --> Create Account : User creates an account
Create Account --> Logged In : User logs in

Logged In --> Apply for Visa : User applies for a visa, makes payment and application is accepted
Apply for Visa --> View Status : User views the status
View Status --> Check Status : User checks the status
Check Status --> Give Feedback : User gives feedback
Give Feedback --> Final State : User logs out

Logged In --> Cancel Application : User cancels an application
Logged In --> Modify Details : User modifies their details
Modify Details --> View Details : User views their details
View Details --> View Purpose : User views the purpose of the application based on document check, visa is either approved or rejected and status is updated
View Purpose --> Final State : User logs out

@enduml
